# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Claude — `.claude/` at the repo root is for machine-local Claude state.
# Project-level config (settings.json, skills, agents) belongs in `dot-claude/`
# and is symlinked into ~/.claude/ by `dot sync`. Everything in `.claude/`
# is gitignored to avoid drift.
.claude/

# Secrets resolve through `op run --` / op:// references, never a file (see
# CLAUDE.md). `.npmrc` is gitignored at the user-config level because per-project
# `.npmrc`s belong to those projects' repos (with op:// refs if they need
# credentials). A user-level `.npmrc` would mostly hold registry-auth
# state we don't want bleeding across projects.
.npmrc

# Transient/generated
Brewfile.lock.json

# Generated audit reports (gnar audit plugin) — regenerate on demand, not tracked.
audit/

# Machine-specific overrides
dot-claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/settings.local.json
